title: Wet Playground at Northpoint City
blurb: Your family fun starts here at Northpoint City!
description: Have a splashing good time at Northpoint City Level 4 (North Wing) as your little ones swoosh down the water slides. Let them soak in fun under our exciting tipping buckets. Do remember to bring along extra sets of clothes and towels for your little ones, or just take the chance to shop for a brand new set in Northpoint!
